This is a game i programmed as a project for a curse in c++ programming class.

Things you need to install on your computer more then only a standard c++ compiler:
	go to www.sfml-dev.org/download/sfml/2.1/ and download the right version
	for you operative system.
	NOTE: if you use ubuntu 13.10 I want you to follow this to installit instead:
		http://sfmlcoder.wordpress.com/2011/08/16/building-sfml-2-0-with-make-for-gcc/

2014-03-22:
	fixed bug with gameover/winner text after game ended.
